    <item>
      <title>linux底下遠端遙控&amp;管理的好用系統 Meshcentral / Remote Management &amp; control system Meshcentral</title>
      <link>https://blog.cowbay.org/p/linux%E5%BA%95%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%A0%E7%AB%AF%E9%81%99%E6%8E%A7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E7%94%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-meshcentral-/-remote-management-control-system-meshcentral/</link>
